name: LAM (ramdayo) style LoRA
description:
LAM is an incredible artist. Please support them if possible.

https://www.pixiv.net/en/users/17429

Capable of producing men as well.

This LoRA specializes in upper body shots and is best used with simple backgrounds. It can produce intense, vibrant colors and effects. It's also great at generating fangs with close-up shots. Eyes will not accurately reproduce LAM's works, nor will the shading.

One thing to mention is that LAM's works tend to use halftone shading, and is not accurately represented by the AI. Use (halftone:1.5) in the negatives to control for it, but this isn't a guarantee.

You can also add "halftone" in the prompt if you want to see how it looks.

Works fine at 1 weight. Lower if needed.

Full bodies don't fare well, but you're welcome to try.

recommended tags:

  • close-up

  • upper body

  • multicolored eyes

  • two-tone hair

  • an eye color

  • glowing eyes

  • (literally any kind of flowers)

  • (your choice of color) light particles

  • facial marks

  • makeup

  • (color) eyeshadow

modelVersions.name: V4
modelVersions.description:
Updated with better knowledge on how to make a LORA.

Reduced filesize, better results.

Now more modular.

Can now opt in for eyeshadow and facial marks.

Halftone shading can now be better controlled for by using the "halftone" tag.
